                "image": "https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1652281333p5/2345.jpg"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 216,
            "author_id": 115,
            "quote": "The one you love and the one who loves you are never, ever the same person.",
            "tags": "life, love,",
            "created_at": "2023-05-24T08:31:34.073945+00:00",
            "book_authors": {
                "id": 115,
                "slug": "chuck-palahniuk",
                "name": "Chuck Palahniuk",
                "image": "https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1391203076p5/2546.jpg"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 233,
            "author_id": 36,
            "quote": "When we love, we always strive to become better than we are. When we strive to become better than we are, everything around us becomes better too.",
            "tags": "hope, inspiration, love, santiago,",
            "created_at": "2023-05-24T08:31:34.073945+00:00",
            "book_authors": {
                "id": 36,
                "slug": "paulo-coelho",
                "name": "Paulo Coelho",
                "image": "https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1201840056p5/566.jpg"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 242,
            "author_id": 284,
            "quote": "I no longer believed in the idea of soul mates, or love at first sight. But I was beginning to believe that a very few times in your life, if you were lucky, you might meet someone who was exactly right for you. Not because he was perfect, or because you were, but because your combined flaws were arranged in a way that allowed two separate beings to hinge together.",
            "tags": "love, relationships, romance,",
            "created_at": "2023-05-24T08:31:34.073945+00:00",
            "book_authors": {
                "id": 284,
                "slug": "lisa-kleypas",
                "name": "Lisa Kleypas",
                "image": "https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1288899037p5/27847.jpg"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 253,
            "author_id": 36,
            "quote": "One is loved because one is loved. No reason is needed for loving.",
            "tags": "love,",
            "created_at": "2023-05-24T08:31:34.073945+00:00",
            "book_authors": {
                "id": 36,
                "slug": "paulo-coelho",
                "name": "Paulo Coelho",
                "image": "https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1201840056p5/566.jpg"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 262,
            "author_id": 223,
            "quote": "When I despair, I remember that all through history the way of truth and love have always won. There have been tyrants and murderers, and for a time, they can seem invincible, but in the end, they always fall. Think of it--always.",
            "tags": "despair, evil, goodness, inspirational, love, sadness, truth, victory,",
            "created_at": "2023-05-24T08:31:34.073945+00:00",
            "book_authors": {
                "id": 223,
                "slug": "mahatma-gandhi",
                "name": "Mahatma Gandhi",
                "image": "https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1356810912p5/5810891.jpg"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 264,
            "author_id": 3,
            "quote": "In vain have I struggled. It will not do. My feelings will not be repressed. You must allow me to tell you how ardently I admire and love you.",
            "tags": "love, mr-darcy,",
            "created_at": "2023-05-24T08:31:34.073945+00:00",
            "book_authors": {
                "id": 3,
                "slug": "jane-austen",
                "name": "Jane Austen",
                "image": "https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1651510251p5/1265.jpg"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 269,
            "author_id": 89,
            "quote": "Sometimes you have to be apart from people you love, but that doesn't make you love them any less. Sometimes you love them more.",
